OL,3,CCardiff to re-launch e-bike hire after
OL,4,Cprevious scheme axed due to vandalism
OL,6,FThe proposed new scheme follows the
OL,7,Fprevious Nextbike programme, which ran
OL,8,Fin Cardiff and the Vale of Glamorgan
OL,9,Fbetween 2018 and 2023. That hire
OL,10,Fscheme was eventually suspended due to
OL,11,Fhigh levels of vandalism and theft.
OL,13,F3,000 bikes were stolen or vandalised
OL,14,Fduring the scheme's operation, leaving
OL,15,Fonly a third of the fleet available
OL,16,Ffor use, Cardiff Council said at the
OL,17,Ftime.
