OL,3,CCardiff to re-launch e-bike hire after
OL,4,Cprevious scheme axed due to vandalism
OL,6,FUnder the new proposals, all the bikes
OL,7,Fare set to be electric, which the
OL,8,FCouncil says makes them "more robust,
OL,9,Fless likely to be vandalised, and
OL,10,Frequire less maintenance."
OL,12,FThere are also plans for the bikes to
OL,13,Fbe parked in designated "geo-fenced"
OL,14,Fareas ` virtual zones that ensure
OL,15,Fbikes can only be left in approved
OL,16,Flocations ` in order to help keep
OL,17,Fpavements clear.
